{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"0a110894-5712-42b3-8b2d-ef7f5e6e4ed1","content":"`.testsettings` files are **not supported** by `dotnet test` — they're a legacy Visual Studio format. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your file contains and how each setting maps:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout = 30000` | `<MSTest><TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` |\n| Code Coverage DataCollector | `<DataCollectors>` section |\n| AssemblyResolution/LoadContext | Default behavior in modern MSTest — no action needed |\n\nLet me create the replacement `.runsettings` file:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01NxZ6YsmegmeoXT6YKiyxMR","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-b6f06a4703af482d9a7168f16118a5c6/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.Coverage.DynamicCoverageDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-b6f06a4703af482d9a7168f16118a5c6/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"b6001402-9c28-496b-8e31-02def60d8d33","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has an MSTest v3 project with a `.testsettings` file. `.testsettings` files are a legacy format that is not supported by modern MSTest / dotnet test. They need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file.\n\nLet me look at what's in their `.testsettings`:\n1. **Assembly resolution** with `useLoadContext=\"true\"` — this is default behavior in modern MSTest, no migration needed.\n2. **TestTimeout of 30000ms** — needs to move to `.runsettings` under `<MSTest><TestTimeout>`.\n3. **Code Coverage data collector** — needs to move to `.runsettings` under `<DataCollectionRunSettings><DataCollectors>`.\n\n\nNow I'll create the `.runsettings` file with these settings and remove the reference to the old `.testsettings` format, since `dotnet test` doesn't support it anymore.","outputTokens":787,"requestId":"5C2A:3E11E8:20AF3E3:25A8D05:69F56182"},"id":"d6b46f30-a06f-4e06-9ed2-f00657f1733d","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:29:40.045Z","parentId":"fe5f1035-512a-4cf8-b81a-203d7e33c8df"}
